ANGELES CITY CONTROLLER; LOS ANGELES -- FINANCES; AUDITS; LOS ANGELES CITY 
TREASURER; FAR EAST NATIONAL BANK; TASK FORCE FOR AFRICA LOS ANGELES RELATIONS; 
TUTTLE, RICK 
</P>
