batting coach Champ Summers survey the field before Friday's game in Detroit. 
Associated Press; Photo, Dallas Green manages his last game for the Yankees, a 
2-1 win over the Tigers in Detroit Thursday night. He was fired Friday. United 
Press International; Photo, Bucky Dent 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
