IRANIAN FLOODS KILL 1 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
NICOSIA, Cyprus 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Floods in Iran's West Azerbaijan province have killed one person and caused 
heavy damage to livestock, homes, and power plants, the Islamic Republic News 
Agency said Friday in a report monitored in Nicosia. 
</P>
</TEXT>
